        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), without hope of recovery. This character of a malicious mischief-maker would seem to be especially hateful to God; it is described in like terms in Psalms 64 and a similar fate foretold of it; in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Proverbs 6:19",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " also it is held up as the very worst of the seven detestable things there mentioned.",
        "children": []
      },
