        "class": "",
        "text": "15. Suddenness aggravates evil (compare Pr 6:11; 29:1).",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "calamity—literally, \"a crushing weight.\"",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "broken—shivered as a potter's vessel; utterly destroyed (Ps 2:9).",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
