  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Therefore shall his calamity come suddenly,.... Unthought of and unexpected: he that deviseth mischief to others secretly shall have no warning of his own ruin, nor time and means of preventing it; the destruction of antichrist will be sudden, and of all wicked men at the coming of Christ, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Thessalonians 5:3",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "suddenly shall he be broken without remedy; or, \"and there shall be no healing\" (b): his bones will be broken to pieces, and there will be no cure for him; or he shall be like an earthen vessel, which, when broke, cannot be put together again. The ruin of wicked men is sudden, inevitable, and irreparable; so antichrist will \"come to his end, and none shall help him\", Daniel 11:45. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "suddenly shall he be broken without remedy; or, \"and there shall be no healing\" (b): his bones will be broken to pieces, and there will be no cure for him; or he shall be like an earthen vessel, which, when broke, cannot be put together again. The ruin of wicked men is sudden, inevitable, and irreparable; so antichrist will \"come to his end, and none shall help him\", ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Daniel 11:45",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". ",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(b)  \"et non sanitas\", Pagninus, Montanus; \"curatio\", Junius & Tremellius; \"medicina\", Piscator, Cocceius. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "(b)  \"et non sanitas\", Pagninus, Montanus; \"curatio\", Junius & Tremellius; \"medicina\", Piscator, Cocceius. ",
            "children": []
